comments: Hield (SAC) engages and disengages with Melton (MEM) as he moves above the free throw line.

Replay review of the foul called on Fox (SAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Fox (SAC) maintains legal guarding position as he moves along Morant's (MEM) path and absorbs the contact.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes incidental arm contact with Giles III (SAC) during the jump ball.
Morant (MEM) makes marginal contact with his off-arm to Joseph's (SAC) midsection as he releases along the perimeter.
Clarke (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in Joseph's (SAC) path and does not deliver the contact.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) side during his drive.
Giles III (SAC) establishes and maintains a legal guarding position in Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path and absorbs the contact as Jackson Jr. drives through his body.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) as he drives inside the perimeter and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Brooks (MEM) makes marginal contact with Giles III (SAC) as the two move toward the loose ball.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) side at the end of Jackson Jr.'s dribble and releases as he enters his upward shooting motion.
Brooks (MEM) commits the take foul on Fox (SAC).
Fox (SAC) dislodges the ball from Morant (MEM) prior to making marginal body contact.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes contact with Giles III's (SAC) right wrist/forearm that affects his dunk attempt.
Brooks (MEM) commits the take foul on Fox (SAC).
Giles III (SAC) makes contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) midsection/right arm during rebounding.
Bazemore (SAC) makes incidental high-five contact with Melton's (MEM) hand after the release of his jump shot attempt and does not affect his ability to follow-through naturally.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) delivers contact to Hield's (SAC) backside after he receives the pass.
Clarke (MEM) commits the take foul on Joseph (SAC).
Bazemore (SAC) briefly has his arms around Clarke's (MEM) upper half before correcting.
Barnes (SAC) makes contact across Melton's (MEM) left hand/wrist at the start of his upward shooting motion. The contact occurs prior to Barnes making any contact with the ball.
Clarke (MEM) commits the take foul on Hield (SAC).
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes marginal contact with Barnes' (SAC) upper half after the release of the free throw. Barnes' reaction is not consistent with the amount of contact.
Morant (MEM) steps over the plane of the free throw line prior to when the ball makes contact with the basket ring.
Joseph (SAC) commits the take foul on Morant (MEM). The contact occurs prior to the start of Morant's upward shooting motion.
Morant (MEM) commits the take foul on Hield (SAC).
